_pdbx_nmr_sample_details.contents
'1.47mM RING domain U-13C,15N; 20mM d-Tris-HCl(pH7.0); 100mM NaCl; 1mM d-DTT; 0.02% NaN3; 0.05mM ZNCl2;  0.05mM EDTA; 90% H2O, 10% D2O'
